{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/KIRO-_-CHLOE--THE-BEGINNING-OF-THE-END.png?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Ties-Soul-Link.jpg?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After an unfortunate accident, <strong>Kiro and Chloe</strong> are abruptly separated, after having been together almost since their first days of life. This causes<strong> Kiro</strong> to become completely weakened and <strong>Chloe</strong> to fall ill. Kiro will have to find the way to <strong>Chloe</strong> to save both his friend and himself. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/THE-ULTIMATE-BOND--THE-SOUL-LINK.png?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Kiro-Chloe.gif?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Soul Link</strong> is a delicate symbiotic, natural, and spiritual connection between a human being and another animal species. It is a relationship in which both beings share sensations, emotions, and the same vital essence, without losing their individuality in terms of thought. Not much is known about the <strong>Soul Link</strong>. Scientists make discoveries day by day. However, they are unaware that the key to understanding this phenomenon lies in the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/KIRO\u2019s-ABILITIES.png?t=1737543901\" /><strong>Kiro can use swords, armors, magics, and abilities. TIES: Soul Link</strong> features a slot-based skill system, allowing for extensive customization and enabling players to adopt their preferred playstyle. The weapon <strong>Kiro</strong> uses to attack is a sword, though there will be a wide variety of models that will increase <strong>Kiro\u2019s</strong> attack power or grant new abilities. Kiro will have equipable armors that protect him from attacks and add abilities or resistance to different magics.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Kiro-Abilities.gif?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The equipable magics are called <strong>\u201cRunes\u201d </strong>and can be swapped to create combinations that best suit the player\u2019s style. Additionally, there will be new abilities to unlock, they can be found during his adventure in the vast world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/DISCOVER-THE-2097\u2019s-WORLDS.png?t=1737543901\" />Year 2097. Four decades have passed since humanity managed to survive the effects of <strong>climate change.</strong> Humans are making their way in a new world shaped by nature and machines. Travel through the different cities where cyberpunk urban landscapes blend with Nordic ruins, Japanese culture, Greek mythology, and Persian influences. Discover new routes and hidden areas to reveal new secrets, collectibles and puzzles that you will have to solve in order to improve your abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/TiesSoulLink.gif?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout each city, players will find <strong>shops and establishments</strong> where they can buy, sell, or upgrade equipment, places to recover health, or simply relax and talk with the residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Shops.png?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/WHATEVER-IT-TAKES-TO-SAVE-CHLOE.png?t=1737543901\" />During his epic journey, Kiro will uncover the lost wisdom of the ancient world, knowledge that holds the answers to the mysteries of the future. Yet, his quest demands more than discovery; it will require him to make choices that will shape the course of his destiny. Be prepared, he will do anything to save his best friend. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Ties-Soul-Link-2.jpg?t=1737543901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/Soul-Link.png?t=1737543901\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2600730?t=1737543901","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737543901","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/ab55e8cd56f247792b6c87d8a345f7e81ce61c9a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737543901","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/ab55e8cd56f247792b6c87d8a345f7e81ce61c9a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737543901","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3024290,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600730/extras/KIR